# ============================================================
# .gitignore raíz — CypherplatoSesion3
# Aplica a solucion1/, solucion2/ y solucion3/
# ============================================================

# --- Dependencias ---
**/node_modules/
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.*
**/.yarn/*
!**/.yarn/patches
!**/.yarn/plugins
!**/.yarn/releases
!**/.yarn/versions

# --- Build / Output de Next.js ---
**/.next/
**/out/
**/build/
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/next-env.d.ts

# --- Testing ---
**/coverage/

# --- Variables de entorno (NUNCA subir claves) ---
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# --- Logs de depuración ---
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/.pnpm-debug.log*

# --- Docker volumes / datos persistentes de ChromaDB ---
**/chroma-data/
**/chroma_data/

# --- Archivos de IDE y sistema operativo ---
**/.DS_Store
**/*.pem
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/

# --- Claude Code / Cursor (configuración local del desarrollador) ---
**/.claude/settings.local.json


# --- Vercel ---
**/.vercel/

# --- Lock de skills (específico de Claude Code, no compartible) ---
**/skills-lock.json
